Presenting the cheque was Iman Cummings, Director of Communications and Business Development at the Corum Group.

By 2030, floods are expected to affect 147 million people a year at a cost of over $700 billion dollars. With the right early warning systems, most flood impacts are avoidable. Earth is changing... dramatically...

The entire solar system is...

We are in the middle of a pole shift...

Countless wildlife have already perished because of the electromagnetic anomalies sweeping our skies and oceans...

Birds falling out of the sky in flocks...creatures of the sea beaching themselves for no apparent reason...

I know what is happening...

And so do the elite...

All of this nwo agenda stuff is related to the earth changes that are happening that are beyond our control....

They know crops are failing....they know cold and famine and war are coming...

And they have been preparing to survive underground in their luxury bunkers...

That leaves the protection of the People to us...warriors...

The coasts will be hit the worst...

Get away from major cities...

Sinkholes and earthquakes will be become more rampant...

As volcanic activity across the planet has already dramatically increased...

The signs in the heavens have been many and only the blind cannot see what is at hand...

The Ancients left warnings in stone megaliths that would stand the test of time for a reason...

Our solar system bares the asteroid belts from destroyed planets for a reason...

This knowledge is in your blood no matter how much you try to deny it...

Your ancestors survived the last time this thing came around and so can you...

Trust your intuition...

Gather your tribe...

And you if want to be apart of mine just slide on into my dms...

Most of the 5d people are content dying and ascending or whatever and that's cool...

But that's not me. 

I was born to rebuild the cult of Neith...
